(3000, 'Kill 25 Cokris', N'Hunt down 25 Cokris in Ruinen Village
Reward:
97 500 EXP', 'Greetings adventurer. I have a quest for you that you can either do alone or together in a party with others. Either way you''ll have to slay 25 Cokris in Ruinen Village.
What do you say? Will you do it?
Objective:
Kill 25 Cokris in Ruinen Village.
Reward:
97 500 EXP', N'Best of luck. Come back when you kill 25 Cokris in Ruinen Village to claim your reward.
If you want to cancel an ongoing quest, right-click on the quest bubble in the top left of your screen.
You''ll have to cancel your current quest from me, before you can take up a different one.', 'Good job adventurer, here is your reward.', 2, 1, 0, 15, 150, 0, 0, 0, '6', '1028', '', 4, '', '', 0, 178, 178, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(9007, 'Novice #7', N'Hunt down 30 Scorpions in Refuge of the Ancients
Reward: 
50 000 Gold
100 000 EXP', N'Hello again. Did you know that a regular scorpion sting can be lethal? Now just imagine what happens when they mutate and grow to almost the same size as you.
If you feel up to the task, I will happily let you reduce their numbers. What do you say?
Objective: Kill 30 Scorpions in Refuge of the Ancients
Reward: 
50 000 Gold
100 000 EXP', N'Remember, you can find these Scorpions in Refuge of the Ancients.
Once you have slain the Scorpions return to me!
TIP: Your total kills are displayed in the little bubbles in the top left corner of your screen.', 'It seems you you are triumphant once again. They could really use your kind of tenacity in Ruinen Village. Head north, through Castle of the Lost. They are situated in a merchants camp in the northwest of Ruinen Village.', 2, 1, 0, 15, 150, 0, 0, 0, '4', '1032', '', 1, '9006', '', 150, 150, 150, 0, '1,2,3,4,9', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
