(9004, 'Novice #4', N'Hunt down 10 Cyclops in Acasia Forest
Reward:
5,000 Gold
40,000 EXP', N'Hello again. You have probably seen these one-eyed giants about. They are what is known as Cyclops, and are very dangerous.
I''ve already sent other adventurers to deal with them, but none of them came back.
I don''t know if you are ready for this, but I would very much appreciate it if you gave it a shot.
Objective: Kill 20 Cyclops in Acasia Forest
Reward:
5,000 Gold
40,000 EXP', N'Remember, you can find these Cyclops in Acasia Forest.
Once you''ve slain 20 Cyclops return to me!
TIP: Your total kills are displayed in the little bubbles in the top left corner of your screen.', 'Whoa, that''s amazing. I cannnot believe you succeeded where so many have failed. It seems you are tougher than I presumed.', 2, 1, 0, 10, 150, 0, 0, 0, '0', '47', '', 1, '9003', '', 150, 150, 150, 0, '1,2,3,4,9', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(9005, 'Novice #5', N'Hunt down 50 Monsters in Acasia Forest
Reward:
10 000 Gold
75 000 EXP
20 Medium Health Potions', N'Hello again. You finally came back! Miscellaneous Store, Lynn has been requesting your help.
Until recently the area surrounding the water mill was quite peaceful but now it''s become overpopulated with monsters.
She wants you to take out a considerable number of them, this should keep her safe for a while. If you do this for her she''ll give you 20 medium health potions.
Objective: Kill 50 Monsters in Acasia Forest
Reward:
10 000 Gold
75 000 EXP
20 Medium Health Potions', N'Remember, you can find these monsters in Acasia Forest.
Once you''ve slain 50 return to me!
TIP: Your total kills are displayed in the little bubbles in the top left corner of your screen.', 'You have made the area so much safer! Thanks to you Lynn''s shop can open again. As a token of her gratitude she left some potions for you.', 2, 1, 0, 10, 150, 0, 0, 0, '0', '0', '', 1, '9004', '', 150, 150, 150, 0, '1,2,3,4,9', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(9006, 'Novice #6', N'Hunt down 30 Skeletons in Refuge of the Ancients
Reward: 
20 000 Gold
100 000 EXP', 'Hello again. The aura of corruption is strong in Refuge of the Ancients, the dead are coming back to life. You won''t be able to exterminate them entirely, but please try to take out 30.
What do you say? Will you do it?
Objective: Kill 30 Skeletons in Refuge of the Ancients
Reward: 
20 000 Gold
100 000 EXP', N'Remember, you can find these Skeletons in Refuge of the Ancients.
Once you''ve slain 30 return to me!
TIP: Your total kills are displayed in the little bubbles in the top left corner of your screen.', 'Did you really kill that many of them? This is terrific news. The fewer undead, the better.', 2, 1, 0, 10, 150, 0, 0, 0, '4', '46', '', 1, '9005', '', 150, 150, 150, 0, '1,2,3,4,9', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1990, 'Granny''s Delivery', N'Bring the cake to Albus P.W.B. Dumbledore in Ricarten
Reward:
500 Gold', N'Ah, young adventurer, would you be willing to help an old lady?
I made my dear friend Albus this cake, but with these old bones I can''t risk traveling too much. I don''t want to break a hip.
Would you be so kind as to bring this to him in Ricarten? He''s usually enjoying the view from the bridge.
Objective: Deliver the Cake to Albus in Ricarten
Reward:
500 Gold', 'Please hurry, adventurer. Albus P.W.B. Dumbledore is waiting in Ricarten.', N'Hello there, young one.
Please send her my best regards and she will reward you with a Mystic Crystal.
Crystals can be used to summon a random monster as your ally or can be sold for a profit.
Objective: Return to Molly, the granny in Phillai
Reward:
Mystic Crystal', 0, 1, 0, 1, 150, 600, 0, 0, '0', '', '', 1, '', '', 71, 71, 130, 1991, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
