(8017, 'Bonus #1', N'Meet Boss Hunter, William in Ricarten or Phillai
Reward:
5 000 Gold', 'Hi there. I see you''ve grown a lot stronger.
I think it''s time for you to meet Boss Hunter, William in Ricarten or Phillai. He gathers information on the whereabouts of bosses.
William will have you hunting down bosses for gold.
Bosses spawn once every hour. You will notice a timer for this above your minimap.
If there is no timer then the map you are on does not have a boss.
TIP: Press F10 to bring up the settings window, here you can check when the next boss spawns from town.
Objective: Meet Boss Hunter, William in Ricarten or Phillai
Reward:
5 000 Gold', 'Pay a visit to Boss Hunter, William. He and his twin brother are located in Ricarten and Phillai!', N'Hey there, are you looking for a real challenge?
I provide quests that will have you hunt down bosses one by one allover Priston. Once you''ve taken them out, and you come back alive, I''ll reward you appropriately.
If you like you could take on a boss challenge right now.
Return to Instructor Millie after you reach level 10 for further instructions.', 0, 1, 0, 5, 1000, 0, 0, 0, '0', '', '', 1, '', '', 168, 168, 164, 0, '5,6,7,8,10', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1508, 'The New Island', 'Kill monsters at Lost Island', 'Slay those monsters, you are our savior!', N'Hurry up! we are all ready to dock, 
just waiting you to clear the Island.', N'You are such a helpful warrior, now we can 
research about that ancient civilization, 
looks like they worshiped some kind of tower, 
anyway, here''s your reward.', 0, 1, 0, 100, 10000, 0, 0, 0, '37', '0', '', 4, '', '', 0, 133, 133, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(9017, 'Introduction Complete', N'Head to Ruinen Village and talk to the Ruinen Kiosk
Reward:
Raident Force', 'Well done, you''ve really proven your mettle.
Your adventure will now take you to Ruinen village. After this final introduction I''ll no longer be your guide, however you should know that you''ll find Daily quest masters in every region and near/in every dungeon floor. And don''t forget about the Lone Wolf quests and Boss Quests that you can take up in Ricarten and Phillai.
It was nice to meet you. Best of luck.
TIP: Before you can Rank-Up you need to learn every skill available.
Objective: Talk to Ruinen Kiosk in Ruinen Village
Reward:
Raident Force', 'It''s time to stand on your own two legs now, adventurer. Head to Ruinen and take the next step in your adventure.', N'Oh Hi there!
Welcome to Ruinen Village, I''m the Ruinen Kiosk. This lovely little lady will provide you with the potions you''ll require to face the dangerous monsters that surround us.
Oh, the Instructor send you, did she? Well that means you''re ready for the real deal! You can help out people in the village by taking daily quests from the daily quest masters now.
Take this, it''s a Raident Force which can be used to temporarily increase your power, use it to help us here in Ruinen Village!
I hope to see you again soon, sweetie!', 2, 1, 0, 15, 150, 0, 0, 0, '0', '', '', 1, '9007', '', 150, 150, 124, 0, '1,2,3,4,9', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
