(1501, 'Warehouse #1', N'Present a Figon Crystal to Lavendar in Phillai
Reward:
Warehouse Page 2', N'Howdy.
Let me get straight to the point. I''ve been hearing stories about crystals that contain monsters in them.
I''m not sure whether it''s a myth or not, but it would be astounding if it were true.
If you can show me a Figon Crystal I''ll compensate you with additional warehouse storage space.
Do we have a deal?
HINT: If you got a Figon Crystal from another player, throw it on the ground and pick it up, for it to count as having found one.
Objective: Show a Figon Crystal to Lavendar in Phillai
Reward:
Warehouse Page 2', 'It doesn''t seem like you found a Figon Crystal. Maybe they don''t exist after all?
Stay safe out there.', N'Howdy, you actually found one?!
So it was actually no mere myth! Some Figons have actually been captured inside crystals!
Thank you for showing this to me. You can keep it.
Here is the additional warehouse storage space I promised. Giving you twice the storage space that you had before.', 4, 1, 0, 40, 150, 0, 0, 0, '-1', '', 'gp106', 1, '', '', 90, 90, 90, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2013, 'A Test of Loneliness', 'Kill 40 Monsters in Abyss of the Sea', 'Are you strong? how about you prove it to me? Hunt 40 Monster at Abyss of the Sea with no help from anyone and then come back to me, if you are indeed strong you will be able to do it.', 'You will not give up, wont you?', 'Wow, you are really strong i guess, here is your reward.', 0, 0, 0, 125, 1000, 7200, 2, 3600, '59', '0', '', 7, '', '', 0, 154, 154, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1648, 'Warehouse Quest #2', 'Meet Miscellaneous Store, Cindy at Gallubia Valley', N'Hello!  Its been a while since i last asked you a favor but could you help me with it?
Some time ago Cindy helped me with some problems that i had so now i own her a favor, she is asking me to help her now but i can''t leave my job here this time.
Can you help her in my place? if you do i shall give some more space on your Warehouse for free!
Objective: Meet Miscellaneous Store, Cindy at Gallubia Valley
', '', N'I need someone to help me, on the process of making these potions i need to go to Ice Mine and gather lots of materials but those monsters wont let me do it.
Please Hunt some of them for me so i can gather peacefully next time.
After killing them Tell Mr.Arent that next time he should come and deal with his favors.
Objective: 
Kill 20 Undead Miners
Kill 20 undead Managers
Kill 10 Tarantulikas
Kill 5 Mine Golems
Reward: Warehouse Page #3
', 0, 1, 0, 120, 10000, 0, 0, 0, '0', '', '', 1, '1641', '', 114, 114, 147, 1649, '1,2,3,4,9', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6000, 'Zzangpy - Garden of Freedom / RttW', N'Boss Challenge
Hunt down Zzangpy in Garden of Freedom or Road to the Wind
Reward:
5 000 Gold
25 000 EXP', N'Greetings adventurer. There have been sightings of a Zzangpy in Garden of Freedom and Road to the Wind.
Will you take this boss down for the safety of our people?
TIP: You can combine two parties into a raid to hunt a boss down with up to 12 players.
Objective:
Kill Zzangpy in Garden of Freedom or Road to the Wind
Reward:
5 000 Gold
25 000 EXP', N'Now go, and defeat that Zzangpy!
If you want to cancel an ongoing quest, right-click on the quest bubble in the top left of your screen. 
You''ll have to cancel your current quest from me, before you can take up a different one.', 'Incredible! You beat the boss! Here is your reward.', 4, 1, 0, 1, 14, 0, 0, 0, '-1', '1156', '', 4, '', '', 0, 164, 164, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1650, 'Warehouse Quest #2', 'Meet Miscellaneous Store, Cindy at Gallubia Valley', N'Hello!  Its been a while since i last asked you a favor but could you help me with it?
Some time ago Cindy helped me with some problems that i had so now i own her a favor, she is asking me to help her now but i can''t leave my job here this time.
Can you help her in my place? if you do i shall give some more space on your Warehouse for free!
Objective: Meet Miscellaneous Store, Cindy at Gallubia Valley
', '', N'I need someone to help me, on the process of making these potions i need to go to Ice Mine and gather lots of materials but those monsters wont let me do it.
Please Hunt some of them for me so i can gather peacefully next time.
After killing them Tell Mr.Lavendar that next time he should come and deal with his favors.
Objective: 
Kill 20 Undead Miners
Kill 20 undead Managers
Kill 10 Tarantulikas
Kill 5 Mine Golems
Reward: Warehouse Page #3
', 0, 1, 0, 120, 10000, 0, 0, 0, '0', '', '', 1, '1643', '', 90, 90, 147, 1651, '5,6,7,8,10', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1652, 'Protect the village!', N'Hunt down 150 Monsters in Ruinen Village
Reward:
Weapon of your choice
150 000 EXP', N'Hey there friend! Welcome to Ruinen Village!
Ruinen Village is crowded with monsters, making it hard to settle down here. Would you decrease their numbers for us? If you can kill about 150 monsters around here we''d be very grateful.
Our Blacksmith Ruga will prepare something useful for you for when you return!
Objective: Kill 150 Monsters in Ruinen Village
Reward:
Weapon of your choice
150 000 EXP', 'We''re still severely outnumbered by these monsters. Go and show them who''s boss!', 'Whoa! You''ve done it!
You are incredible, you have my undying gratitude.
Here are the weapons, go ahead and pick one.', 2, 1, 0, 15, 150, 0, 0, 0, '6', '0', '', 1, '', '', 120, 121, 121, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(9008, 'Beginning #1', N'Meet Blacksmith Gus in Ricarten
Reward:
Starter weapon of your choice', 'Hi there. My name is Annie and I''m here to help guide you through the lands of Priston.
I am going to introduce you to the various inhabitants that may help you in the future. Let''s start shall we?
Meet Blacksmith Gus and let him know I sent you. He will prepare a weapon for you.
TIP: Mouseover then press and hold P to view the perfect version of an item.
Objective: Meet Blacksmith Gus in Ricarten
Reward:
Starter weapon of your choice', 'The minimap in the bottom right corner will show you Blacksmith Gus when you are getting close to him.', N'Splendid! Another new adventurer!
Choose one of these starter weapons to protect yourself against the vile creatures all over the lands of Priston. It''s a dangerous and long road you''ve got ahead of you adventurer!
Make sure to head back to Annie for further instructions.', 0, 1, 0, 1, 1000, 0, 0, 0, '0', '', '', 1, '', '', 150, 150, 96, 0, '1,2,3,4,9', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(9009, 'Beginning #2', N'Meet Miscellaneous Store, Namy in Ricarten
Reward:
10 Mini Health Potions', N'Hi there. Good, I see that Gus has supplied you with a weapon!
In the world of Priston you can use potions to keep yourself alive in combat.
The best person to introduce you to them would be Namy, go to her to receive some minor health potions!
TIP: Mouseover potions in your inventory then press Shift and 1-3 to place them quickly into your action bar.
Objective: Meet Miscellaneous Store, Namy in Ricarten
Reward:
10 Mini Health Potions', 'The minimap in the bottom right corner will show you Namy when you are getting close to her.', N'Oh hi there!
Glad to see new faces around here.
Let me give you some potions, These will keep you safe in combat.
Make sure to drink them when your health points are low! Don''t be afraid to drink plenty of them if you''re in a tight spot!
TIP: You can bind potions to keys 1, 2 and 3 by dragging them into your action bar.
Make sure to head back to Annie for further instructions.', 0, 1, 0, 1, 1000, 0, 0, 0, '0', '', '', 1, '9008', '', 150, 150, 112, 0, '1,2,3,4,9', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(9010, 'Beginning #3', N'Meet Warehouse Keeper, Arent in Ricarten
Reward:
Hopy Crystal', 'Hi there. During your adventures you''ll obtain many items, sometimes too many to bring along with you. You can either sell them to a storefront or open up a personal shop.
If you want the ability to keep more items then you can talk to Warehouse Keeper, Arent for some extra storage space!
TIP: Every 30 minutes a random winner is chosen for the ''OnlineReward'', the winner receives random items or premium items that can be picked up from Item Distributor.
Objective: Meet Warehouse Keeper, Arent in Ricarten
Reward:
Hopy Crystal', 'The minimap in the bottom right corner will show you Arent when you are getting close to him.', N'Salutations. So Annie sent you did she? You want some storage space do ya? Alright, you got it.
What''s that? You were promised a Hopy Crystal? *Sigh* here you go.
TIP: You can use Crystals to summon monsters to fight for you!
Make sure to head back to Annie for further instructions.', 0, 1, 0, 1, 1000, 0, 0, 0, '0', '', '', 1, '9009', '', 150, 150, 114, 0, '1,2,3,4,9', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(9013, 'Beginning #6', N'Hunt down 10 Hopys in Garden of Freedom
Reward:
Lucidy
2 500 EXP', N'Hi there. You seem ready for your first combat challenge now!
Let''s start simple, shall we? Head northeast to the exit of Ricarten and enter into Garden of Freedom, then take down 10 Hopys. I''ll reward you on your return.
TIP: Press and hold A to see and prioritize picking up items.
Objective: Kill 10 Hopys in Garden of Freedom
Reward:
Lucidy
2 500 EXP', N'Remember, you can find these Hopys in the Garden of Freedom just outside of Ricarten.
Once you''ve slain 10 of them you can return to me.
TIP: Your total kills are displayed in the little bubbles in the top left corner of your screen.', 'Marvellous, you''ve slain 10 Hopys!
Did you come across any other adventurers? Did you know that you can use emoticons by entering the commands e1 up to e10 in the chatbox?
Here, have this Lucidy, it will grant you bonus HP and MP regeneration.
Alright, now it''s time for your next challenge.', 2, 1, 0, 1, 1000, 0, 0, 0, '2', '41', '', 1, '9012', '', 150, 150, 150, 0, '1,2,3,4,9', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(9014, 'Beginning #7', N'Hunt down 25 monsters in Garden of Freedom
Reward:
(2x) Round Ring +2 
5 000 EXP', 'Hi there. Since you seem to have completed my previous task with ease, I''m going to increase the difficulty a little for this next one.
Kill any 25 monsters in Garden of Freedom and I''ll give you a little something nice.
Objective: Kill 25 Monsters in Garden of Freedom
Reward:
(2x) Round Ring +2 
5 000 EXP', N'Remember, you can find the Garden of Freedom just outside of Ricarten.
Once you''ve slain 25 monsters return to me (Look for me in Garden of Freedom).
TIP: Your total kills are displayed in the little bubbles in the top left corner of your screen.', 'Spectacular! You''ve slain 25 monsters! You''ve saved the Guards some work today.
I think it''s time to move on to Bamboo Forest as you''ve grown considerably stronger, adventurer.
TIP: Use "M" to enlarge the Map. Bamboo Forest is to the west of Garden of Freedom.', 2, 1, 0, 1, 1000, 0, 0, 0, '2', '0', '', 1, '9013', '', 150, 150, 150, 0, '1,2,3,4,9', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(8009, 'Beginning #1', N'Meet Blacksmith Bartz in Phillai
Reward:
Starter weapon of your choice', 'Hey you, I''m Millie. You seem lost, are you looking for something?
Oh I see, you are one of those new arrivals. Let me help guide you through the city, let''s start with getting you some equipment.
Bring this letter to Blacksmith Bartz, he will set you up with a weapon.
TIP: Mouseover then press and hold P to view the perfect version of an item.
Objective: Meet Blacksmith Bartz in Phillai
Reward:
Starter weapon of your choice', 'You will find Blacksmith Bartz to the east.', 'Ah, Annie sent you for a weapon, did she? Do you know what you''re looking for?
The Knight is at his best with a sword, while the Atalanta excels using a javelin. Magic users such as the Magician and Priestess should be on the lookout for a wand or staff. Last but not least the Shaman uses Phantoms. For the last three you should seek out the Witchcraft Store.
Make sure to head back to Millie for further instructions.', 0, 1, 0, 1, 1000, 0, 0, 0, '0', '', '', 1, '', '', 168, 168, 73, 0, '5,6,7,8,10', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(8010, 'Beginning #2', N'Meet Miscellaneous Store, Phillya in Phillai
Reward: 
10 Mini Health Potions', 'Hey you. You might already be aware of this but it''s dangerous out there.
You should visit Miscellaneous Store, Phillya and ask her for some potions. Be nice to her, she seemed kind of grumpy when I saw her earlier today.
TIP: Mouseover potions in your inventory then press Shift and 1-3 to place them quickly into your action bar.
Objective: Meet Miscellaneous Store, Phillya in Phillai
Reward: 
10 Mini Health Potions', 'You can find Phillya east of here.', 'What''s this? A new arrival? Without any money? Annie!! *shakes fist*
You know what? Fine. Take these potions and don''t forget to keep them on hand, you don''t want to have to rummage through your bag in the middle of a fight.
And remember to come back once you have some money.
TIP: You can bind potions to keys 1, 2 and 3 by dragging them into your action bar.
Make sure to head back to Millie for further instructions.', 0, 1, 0, 1, 1000, 0, 0, 0, '0', '', '', 1, '8009', '', 168, 168, 89, 0, '5,6,7,8,10', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(8011, 'Beginning #3', N'Meet Warehouse Keeper, Lavendar in Phillai
Reward:
Hopy Crystal', 'Hey you. I suggest that you meet Warehouse Keeper, Lavendar. She can help you store items you want to keep but don''t need to carry on you.
If you have items you don''t want to keep you can also sell them to a storefront or open a personal shop.
TIP: Every 30 minutes a random winner is chosen for the ''OnlineReward'', the winner receives random items or premium items that can be picked up from Item Distributor.
Objective: Meet Warehouse Keeper, Lavendar in Phillai
Reward:
Hopy Crystal', 'Head west of here and you''ll find her.', N'Hello, are you looking for more storage space? You came at just the right time since we just lost a client.
Sorry, but we didn''t have time to clean it out. What''s this? It seems the previous tenant left a crystal behind. Here it''s yours.
TIP: You can use Crystals to summon monsters to fight for you!
Make sure to head back to Millie for further instructions.', 0, 1, 0, 1, 1000, 0, 0, 0, '0', '', '', 1, '8010', '', 168, 168, 90, 0, '5,6,7,8,10', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(8012, 'Beginning #4', N'Meet Inventor of Warpgate in Ricarten
Reward:
Leather Boots', N'Hey you. Do you know how a Warp Gate works? 
Well, if you don''t.. you''ll figure it out right? Head north, you will find a Warp Gate there. Use it to go to Ricarten.
Your eyes should meet Inventor of Warpgate near the Warp Gate in Ricarten. He will teach you about teleportation.
TIP: Press Ctrl + End to make screenshots without HUD and Ctrl + Home to include HUD.
Objective: Meet Inventor of Warpgate in Ricarten (Go North to Warp Gate then select Ricarten on the map)
Reward:
Leather Boots', 'Use the warpgate to teleport to Ricarten!', N'Greetings adventurer.
I am the Inventor of the Warp Gate. I can provide you with teleportation wings allowing you to teleport all around the world of Priston!
You will have to bring me a certain amount of gold and the required Crystals for these wings.
TIP: Crystals are obtained by killing monsters.
Make sure to head back to Millie for further instructions.', 0, 1, 0, 1, 1000, 0, 0, 0, '0', '', '', 1, '8011', '', 168, 168, 115, 0, '5,6,7,8,10', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(8013, 'Beginning #5', N'Meet Blacksmith Defrain in Phillai
Reward:
Leather Armlets', N'Hey you. Did you find the Warp Gate okay?
I heard Blacksmith Defrain is making room in his shop, perhaps he will give you something free of charge.
Objective: Meet Blacksmith Defrain in Phillai
Reward:
Leather Armlets', 'You can find Blacksmith Defrain in Phillai.', 'Hey, please excuse the mess, I haven''t had time to clean.
Are you looking for equipment? You can get a pair of these armlets for free since I have too many of them. Additionally, take a look at my wares and see if you want to buy anything.
TIP: You can buy an assortiment of Weapons and Armor from Blacksmiths. Swap between the tabs by pressing the Weapons and Armor icons.
Alright next up it''s time your first monster eradication quest!
Make sure to head back to Millie for further instructions.', 0, 1, 0, 1, 1000, 0, 0, 0, '0', '', '', 1, '8012', '', 168, 168, 74, 0, '5,6,7,8,10', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(9011, 'Beginning #4', N'Meet Inventor of Warpgate in Ricarten
Reward:
Leather Boots', 'Hi there. Don''t worry, we''re almost done here. Just a few more people to meet before the action really begins!
Next up, it''s time for you to visit the Inventor of Warpgate, he will teach you about teleportation. You''ll be given the means to teleport farther as well as a comfy pair of leather boots, because there''s no substitute for walking. You can find him in the south end.
TIP: Press Ctrl + End to make screenshots without HUD and Ctrl + Home to include HUD.
Objective: Meet Inventor of Warpgate in Ricarten
Reward:
Leather Boots', 'You can find the Inventor of Warpgate in the far southern part of Ricarten.', N'Greetings, adventurer. I am the Inventor of Warpgate. I can provide you with teleportation wings allowing you to teleport allover the world of Priston!
You will have to bring me a certain amount of gold and the required Crystals for these wings.
TIP: Crystals are obtained by killing monsters.
Make sure to head back to Annie for further instructions.', 0, 1, 0, 1, 10000, 0, 0, 0, '0', '', '', 1, '9010', '', 150, 150, 115, 0, '1,2,3,4,9', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(9012, 'Beginning #5', N'Meet Blacksmith Goden in Ricarten
Reward:
Leather Armlets', N'Hi there. Now before you head out into the world, you should really meet Blacksmith Goden.
He will provide you with armlets, these help you carry a multitude of potions in your action bar. After this you will be sent on your first fighting challenge!
TIP: Hold Ctrl while right-clicking the potions in your warehouse if you want to take out a specific number (You unlock the warehouse at Level 10). Hold Ctrl + Left Click potions in your inventory to move a specified number.
Objective: Meet Blacksmith Goden in Ricarten
Reward:
Leather Armlets', 'You can find Blacksmith Goden to the west.', 'Well hello there. So you''ve already met most of the other inhabitants of Ricarten, have you? 
Here take these leather armlets, these will allow you to store a respectable number of potions in your action bar.
If you''ve saved up enough gold, you might want to consider purchasing some body armor.
TIP: You can buy an assortiment of Weapons and Armor from Blacksmiths. Swap between the tabs by pressing the Weapons and Armor icons.
Alright then, prepare yourself for your first fighting challenge!
Make sure to head back to Annie for further instructions.', 0, 1, 0, 1, 10000, 0, 0, 0, '0', '', '', 1, '9011', '', 150, 150, 95, 0, '1,2,3,4,9', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(8015, 'Beginning #6', N'Hunt down 10 Rabie in Road to the Wind
Reward:
Lucidy
2 500 EXP', 'Hey you. It seems to me you''re ready for your first combat challenge.
I promise I will start you off with a simple target. Take the Warp Gate in the South, it will lead you to Road to the Wind. Then search for and kill 10 Rabie and return to me. You''ll be rewarded with a Lucidy and an ample amount of experience.
Be careful though, some adventurers have reported seeing North Goblins in Road to the Wind. These monsters are especially dangerous.
TIP: Press and hold A to see and prioritize picking up items.
Objective: Kill 10 Rabie in Road to the Wind
Reward:
Lucidy
2 500 EXP', N'Remember, you can find these Rabie in the Road to the Wind. Take the southern Warp Gate to get there.
Once you''ve slain 10 of them you can return to me. (Meet me in Road to the Wind near the entrance)
TIP: Your total kills are displayed in the little bubbles in the top left corner of your screen.', N'This is great! You managed to slay 10 Rabie.
Did you meet other adventurers to chat with? Did you know you can use emoticons by typing the commands e1 up to e10 in the chatbox?
Here, this is yours. It''s a Lucidy, equipping it will grant you bonus HP and MP regeneration.
Alright, now it''s time for your next challenge.', 2, 1, 0, 1, 1000, 0, 0, 0, '20', '42', '', 1, '8013', '', 168, 168, 168, 0, '5,6,7,8,10', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(8016, 'Beginning #7', N'Hunt down 25 Monsters in Road to the Wind
Reward:
(2x) Round Ring +2 
5 000 EXP', 'Hey you. Very good, you managed to complete the easy task, I''m going to increase the difficulty for this next one.
Kill any 25 monsters in Road to the Wind and you will be rewarded even better than last time.
If you think you are strong enough you could begin hunting the infamous North Goblin for the experience and loot. But it''s up to you.
Objective: Kill 25 Monsters in Road to the Wind
Reward:
(2x) Round Ring +2 
5 000 EXP', N'Remember, you can find these monsters in Road to the Wind.
Once you''ve slain 25 monsters return to me. (Meet me in Road to the Wind near the entrance)
TIP: Your total kills are displayed in the little bubbles in the top left corner of your screen.', N'Thanks to your efforts Road to the Wind is safer now.
When you''re ready for your next quest, you can find me in the middle of Valley of Tranquility.
TIP: Use "M" to enlarge the map. Valley of tranquility is a straight shot south from here.', 2, 1, 0, 1, 1000, 0, 0, 0, '20', '0', '', 1, '8015', '', 168, 168, 168, 0, '5,6,7,8,10', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(3032, 'Kill 40 King Hopies H', N'Hunt down 40 King Hopies in Ancient Prison 3F
Reward:
2 200 000 EXP', 'Greetings adventurer. I have a quest for you that you can either do alone or together in a party with others. Either way you''ll have to slay 40 King Hopies in Ancient Prison 3F.
What do you say? Will you do it?
Objective:
Kill 40 King Hopies in Ancient Prison 3F.
Reward:
2 200 000 EXP', N'Best of luck. Come back when you kill 40 King Hopies in Ancient Prison 3F to claim your reward.
If you want to cancel an ongoing quest, right-click on the quest bubble in the top left of your screen.
You''ll have to cancel your current quest from me, before you can take up a different one.', 'Good job adventurer, here is your reward.', 2, 1, 0, 60, 150, 0, 0, 0, '15', '1111', '', 4, '', '', 0, 191, 191, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(3033, 'Kill 65 Dark Knights', N'Hunt down 65 Dark Knights in Dark Sanctuary
Reward:
2 200 000 EXP', 'Greetings adventurer. I have a quest for you that you can either do alone or together in a party with others. Either way you''ll have to slay 65 Dark Knights in Dark Sanctuary.
What do you say? Will you do it?
Objective:
Kill 65 Dark Knights in Dark Sanctuary.
Reward:
2 200 000 EXP', N'Best of luck. Come back when you kill 65 Dark Knights in Dark Sanctuary to claim your reward.
If you want to cancel an ongoing quest, right-click on the quest bubble in the top left of your screen.
You''ll have to cancel your current quest from me, before you can take up a different one.', 'Good job adventurer, here is your reward.', 2, 1, 0, 65, 150, 0, 0, 0, '26', '1069', '', 4, '', '', 0, 183, 183, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(9000, 'Beginning #8', N'Hunt down 15 Ghosts in Bamboo Forest
Reward:
25 000 EXP', 'Hey you. This isn''t something I tell everyone but, Ghosts are my greatest fear.
Would you please kill 15 of them for me? Thank you in advance!
Objective: Kill 15 Ghosts in Bamboo Forest
Reward:
25 000 EXP', N'Remember, you can press "M" to enlarge the map.
Once you''ve slain 15 Ghosts return to me!
TIP: Your total kills are displayed in the little bubbles in the top left corner of your screen.', 'Phew, I''m really glad you managed to do it. My nerves would''ve gotten to me if I tried. These Ghosts creep me out so much!', 2, 1, 0, 5, 1000, 0, 0, 0, '1', '1015', '', 1, '9014', '', 150, 150, 150, 0, '1,2,3,4,9', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(9001, 'Beginning  #9', N'Hunt down 15 Imps in Bamboo Forest
Reward:
25 000 EXP', N'Hey you. Now I know they tell us not to play with fire but..
I''m still gonna ask you to hunt down 15 Imps because these little fire ball chucking buggers are really getting on my nerves.
Objective: Kill 15 Imps in Bamboo Forest
Reward:
25 000 EXP', N'Remember, you can press "M" to enlarge the map.
Once you''ve slain 15 Imps return to me!
TIP: Your total kills are displayed in the little bubbles in the top left corner of your screen.', 'Well done. That''ll teach those fiery little squirts. You''re starting to show real promise for the future, adventurer!', 2, 1, 0, 5, 1000, 0, 0, 0, '1', '1018', '', 1, '9000', '', 150, 150, 150, 0, '1,2,3,4,9', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(9002, 'Novice #1', N'Meet Skill Master Verkan in Ricarten
Reward:
50 000 EXP', N'Hello again. You have been making great progress.
You''re getting very good at dispatching monsters, and your actions have made the lands of Priston safer.
It''s time for you to meet your Skill Master, Verkan. You can find him in Ricarten. Use the Warp Gate.
You can also return to Ricarten by using an Ether Core. If you don''t own one you can purchase them from Miscellaneous Stores allover Priston.
TIP: You can bind skills by pressing and holding the left or right mouse button and pressing F1 through F8.
Objective: Meet Skill Master Verkan in Ricarten and learn your first skill
Reward:
50 000 EXP', 'Go and meet Skill Master Verkan in Ricarten.', N'Greetings adventurer.
My name is Raymon, I''m the Skill Master for adventurers of the Morion tribe.
I can teach you skills that will make you a stronger and more versatile combatant, able to defeat monsters more effectively!
You can come to me at level 20, 40 and 60 to obtain your Rank-UP Quests.
When you Rank-UP you will have a new tier of skills at your disposal as well as the option to reset your skillpoints for free.
Don''t forget that training your skills here will cost you. And pay mind to how using your skills reduces their cooldown.
Alright, time for you to get back to saving the world of Priston!
Make sure to head back to Millie for further instructions.', 0, 1, 0, 10, 1000, 0, 0, 0, '0', '', '', 1, '9001', '', 150, 150, 109, 0, '1,2,3,4,9', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(8000, 'Beginning #8', N'Hunt down 15 Egans in Valley of Tranquility
Reward: 
25 000 EXP', N'Hey you. The name Valley of Tranquility comes from a long history of being one of the more peaceful lands in Priston.
An influx of Egans, tiny little wizards, is starting to turn this around. Please help us keep this area peaceful.
Objective: Kill 15 Egans in Valley of Tranquility
Reward: 
25 000 EXP', N'Remember, you can press "M" to enlarge the map.
Once you''ve slain 15 Egans return to me!
TIP: Your total kills are displayed in the little bubbles in the top left corner of your screen.', 'Thanks! This was a big help. But we are still gonna need more of your assistance in this matter.', 2, 1, 0, 5, 1000, 0, 0, 0, '19', '1014', '', 1, '8016', '', 168, 168, 168, 0, '5,6,7,8,10', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(8002, 'Novice #1', N'Meet Witchraft Academy, Raymon in Phillai
Reward:
50 000 EXP', N'Hey you.
I can tell you''ve been been honing your skills and your actions have made the lands of Priston safer.
I''d say it''s time for you to meet your Skill Master, you can find Raymon in Phillai.
You can also return to Phillai by using an Ether Core if you don''t own one you can purchase them from Miscellaneous Stores allover Priston.
TIP: You can bind skills by pressing and holding the left or right mouse button and pressing F1 through F8.
Objective: Meet Witchcraft Academy, Raymon in Phillai and learn your first skill
Reward:
50 000 EXP', 'Go on and meet Witchraft Academy, Raymon. He''s in Phillai!', N'Greetings adventurer.
My name is Raymon, I''m the Skill Master for adventurers of the Morion race.
I can teach you skills that will make you stronger and a more versatile combatant, able to defeat monsters more effectively!
You can come to me at level 20, 40 and 60 to obtain your Rank-UP Quests.
When you Rank-UP you will have a new tier of skills at your disposal as well as the option to reset your skillpoints for free.
Don''t forget that training skills will cost you. Practice using your skills to be able to use them more often. Remember that training a skill reduces the cooldown according to its current amount.
Alright, it''s time for you to get back to saving the world of Priston!
Make sure to head back to Millie for further instructions.', 0, 1, 0, 10, 1000, 0, 0, 0, '0', '', '', 1, '8001', '', 168, 168, 87, 0, '5,6,7,8,10', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(8004, 'Novice #3', N'Hunt down 20 North Goblins in Land of Dusk
Reward:
3 000 Gold
50 000 EXP', 'Hey you. I''m glad you''re here. Have you noticed the increase of North Goblins?
They''ve begun to travel together and are scheming to travel to Road of the Wind. Will you reduce their numbers before this happens?
Objective: Kill 20 North Goblins in Land of Dusk
Reward:
3 000 Gold
50 000 EXP', N'Remember, you can find these North Goblins in Land of Dusk.
