(9016, 'Bonus #1', N'Meet Boss Hunter, William in Ricarten or Phillai
Reward:
5 000 Gold', 'Hi there. I see you''ve grown a lot stronger.
I think it''s time for you to meet Boss Hunter, William in Ricarten or Phillai. He gathers information on the whereabouts of bosses.
William will have you hunting down bosses for gold.
Bosses spawn once every hour. You will notice a timer for this above your minimap.
If there is no timer then the map you are on does not have a boss.
TIP: Press F10 to bring up the settings window, here you can check when the next boss spawns from town.
Objective: Meet Boss Hunter, William in Ricarten or Phillai
Reward:
5 000 Gold', 'Go pay a visit to Boss Hunter, William. He and his twin brother are located in Ricarten and Phillai!', N'Hey there, are you looking for a real challenge?
I provide quests that will have you hunt down bosses one by one allover Priston. Once you''ve taken them out, and you come back alive, I''ll reward you appropriately.
If you like you could take on a boss challenge right now.
Return to Instructor Annie after you reach level 10 for further instructions.', 0, 1, 0, 5, 1000, 0, 0, 0, '0', '', '', 1, '', '', 150, 150, 164, 0, '1,2,3,4,9', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(7005, 'Working that summer body!', 'Event Boss Challenge - Castle of the Lost', 'Hey you! I''m sure you want to look beautiful this summer?
Well that''s possible if you help me out first then I''ll give you a Summer Costume. They''re not of the best quality but they look good!
So what i''ll need you to-do is kill Rage of the Desert in Castle of the Lost. I''m sure it''ll be an easy task.
And well... if it''s not that easy,
No pain no gain!
TIP: You can combine two parties into a raid to hunt a boss down with up to 12 players.
Objective:
Kill Rage of the Desert
Reward:
1x Summer Costume', 'Good luck gorgeous!', 'Wait really? You killed the Rage of the Desert? I cannot believe it, well here take the costume you beauty.', 4, 1, 0, 1, 120, 0, 0, 0, '-1', '1468', '', 7, '', '', 218, 218, 218, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
