(8006, 'Novice #5', N'Hunt down 50 Monsters in Land of Dusk
Reward:
10 000 Gold
75 000 EXP
20 Medium Health Potions', N'Hey you. Have you noticed that there is a Warp Gate in the northwest?
Dela''s shop is running out of supplies. She has been waiting for days for a caravan to come through that Warp Gate, to no avail.
She needs your help to clear a path. That way the caravan can safely travel to her shop.
Objective: Kill 50 Monsters in Land of Dusk
Reward:
10 000 Gold
75 000 EXP
20 Medium Health Potions', N'We still need you to a clear a path.
Once you''ve slain 50 Monsters return to me!
TIP: Your total kills are displayed in the little bubbles in the top left corner of your screen.', 'Thanks to you the caravan has been able to supply Dela''s shop. She wanted you to have these potions.
The next quest will put your fire resistance to the test.', 2, 1, 0, 10, 1000, 0, 0, 0, '18', '0', '', 1, '8005', '', 168, 168, 168, 0, '5,6,7,8,10', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
