Reward:
20 000 Gold
100 000 EXP', 'Hey you. We have a serious problem here, you''ll never guess what it is.
It''s the Mutant Trees, these particular trees are launching fireballs on anything that moves, which is a serious fire hazard since this is a forest.
Hurry up, this is a time sensitive mission!
Objective: Kill 30 Mutant Trees in Forest of Spirits
Reward:
20 000 Gold
100 000 EXP', N'Remember, you can find these Mutant Trees in Forest of Spirit.
Once you''ve slain 30 Mutant Trees return to me!
