8 000 000 EXP', 'Greetings adventurer. I have a quest for you that you can either do alone or together in a party with others. Either way you''ll have to slay 80 Avelisk Archers in Railway of Chaos.
What do you say? Will you do it?
Objective:
Kill 80 Avelisk Archers in Railway of Chaos.
Reward:
8 000 000 EXP', N'Best of luck. Come back when you kill 80 Avelisk Archers in Railway of Chaos to claim your reward.
If you want to cancel an ongoing quest, right-click on the quest bubble in the top left of your screen.
You''ll have to cancel your current quest from me, before you can take up a different one.', 'Good job adventurer, here is your reward.', 2, 1, 0, 80, 150, 0, 0, 0, '27', '25', '', 4, '', '', 0, 185, 185, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
